title: Greek Turkey and Rice Skillet
ingredients: 1 Tbsp olive oil,2 cloves garlic,19 oz ground turkey 97% lean,1 tsp dried oregano,1/4 tsp salt,pepper,1 cup long grain white rice,0.25 lb frozen cut leaf spinach,1/3 cup sun dried tomato halves,1/2 cup kalamata olives sliced,1 and half cups chicken broth,handful fresh parsley,1 fresh lemon ,1 oz feta
instructions: 1. Add the olive oil and garlic to a large deep skillet and saute over medium heat for -2 minutes,or until the garlic is fragrant. Add the ground turkey,oregano,salt and pepper to the skillet.Continue to saute until the turkey is cooked through(about 5 minutes.)
